{"Navigation":{"home":"Home","howItWorks":"Recovery Plan","services":"Services","therapists":"Therapists","blog":"Blog","about":"About Us","faq":"FAQ","dashboard":"Dashboard","login":"Log in","register":"Get Started","logout":"Log out","contact":"Contact Us"},"Hero":{"badge":"Your Trusted Mental Health Platform","title1":"Your journey to","title2":"recovery starts here","subtitle":"Connect with top certified consultants and therapists in complete privacy, and take your first steps towards a brighter, more balanced life.","cta":"Start Your First Session","ctaSecondary":"Browse Therapists"},"Footer":{"description":"A secure and easy-to-use Arabic mental health platform. Voice, video, and chat sessions inside the platform with complete privacy.","motto":"Your mental health is a priority, and we are here to help you ✦","quickLinks":"Quick Links","support":"Support & Help","contact":"Contact Us","copyright":"All rights reserved","privacy":"Privacy Policy","terms":"Terms & Conditions"},"About":{"title":"Clear & Noble Mission","desc":"We provide you with a safe and easy mental health experience, starting from your first booking and extending to continuous support step by step.","title2":"Trusted Therapists","desc2":"We carefully select psychologists with accredited certificates, proven track records, and exceptional reviews.","title3":"Absolute Privacy","desc3":"We guarantee complete confidentiality of your data and sessions through end-to-end encryption, giving you full control over your personal info.","whyTitle1":"Certified Therapists","whyDesc1":"A carefully selected team of elite certified specialists","whyTitle2":"Integrated Platform","whyDesc2":"Video, audio, and chat sessions without external apps","whyTitle3":"Flexible Booking","whyDesc3":"Choose your slot and therapist smoothly and simply","whyTitle4":"Fair Pricing","whyDesc4":"Transparent, fair pricing with no hidden fees","vision":"Our Vision & Approach","heading":"Professional mental health care that understands your needs","p1":"We are not just a platform; we are partners in your journey to recovery and growth. We connect you with certified therapists for video, audio, or text sessions entirely within ","p1bold":"our secure, closed environment","p1_2":". No need for external apps, ensuring maximum privacy.","p2":"We strive to provide a streamlined, comfortable service, focusing on complete confidentiality and peace of mind in every detail of your journey.","bullet1":"Exclusively certified and proven therapists","bullet2":"Full encryption of your sessions","bullet3":"Continuous, reliable support whenever needed","valuesHeading":"Our Core Values","valuesTitle1":"Building bridges of","valuesTitle2":"Trust","valuesTitle3":"with our clients","valuesDesc":"Three core values govern every decision we make to ensure we always provide the best for you.","futureVision":"Our Vision for the Future of Mental Health","futureDesc":"To be the first and most trusted choice for those seeking professional Arab mental health support, combining elegance, absolute privacy, and a comfortable experience that makes you feel at home.","cta":"Start your recovery journey","whyChooseUs":"Why thousands choose us?","competitiveAdvantage":"Competitive Advantages","whyChooseUsDesc":"The reasons that make our platform the first destination for mental healthcare."},"HowItWorks":{"step1Title":"Create Account","step1Desc":"Register with your email or social accounts, then complete your profile easily in minutes to customize your experience.","step2Title":"Explore Therapists","step2Desc":"Browse the list of available therapists by specialty, experience, price, and reviews, and choose the most suitable one for your needs.","step3Title":"Choose Session Type","step3Desc":"Choose your preferred method: video (for full visual contact), audio (for more privacy), or text chat (for high flexibility).","step4Title":"Book Appointment","step4Desc":"Select the appropriate date and time from the therapist's available slots and get an instant confirmation email.","step5Title":"Join Session","step5Desc":"At the scheduled time, enter the secure, fully encrypted session room directly from your dashboard without needing external apps.","step6Title":"Follow-up & Support","step6Desc":"Receive feedback from your therapist, track your progress, and communicate continuously inside the platform to ensure your recovery's success.","feat1Title":"Seamless Experience","feat1Desc":"From registration to the session, a single interface carefully designed for your comfort","feat2Title":"Total Security","feat2Desc":"Secret encryption and strict protection for your personal data and therapy sessions","feat3Title":"High Flexibility","feat3Desc":"You control everything: the therapist, the time, and even the type of communication","feat4Title":"Continuous Support","feat4Desc":"We are with you every step of the way with continuous technical support and follow-up","time1Title":"Registration & Selection","time1Time":"5 minutes","time1Desc":"Create an account and choose the right therapist","time2Title":"Book Appointment","time2Time":"2 minutes","time2Desc":"Select the appropriate time and complete booking","time3Title":"Start Therapy","time3Time":"Instantly","time3Desc":"Enter the session at the scheduled time","heroTag":"Recovery Plan","heroTitle":"6 Simple Steps for Recovery","heroDesc":"We designed your journey with us to be smooth, intuitive, and completely comfortable. From registration to the first session, everything is clear and simple.","journeyTag":"Journey Map","journeyTitle":"Your steps to mental comfort","timeEfficiencyTag":"Time Efficiency","timeEfficiencyTitle":"Faster than you imagine","startJourneyTag":"Start Now","startJourneyTitle":"Ready for the first step?","startJourneyDesc":"Don't delay your mental comfort, start your journey now with simple steps and get on the right track.","startJourneyBtn":"Create Free Account","valueTag":"Value","valueTitle":"Why our experience is different?","browseTherapists":"Browse Therapists"},"FAQ":{"heroBadge":"Common Questions","heroTitle":"All the answers you're looking for","heroSubtitle":"We are here to remove any ambiguity and make your journey with us clear and reassuring from the first step.","catSelection":"Selection","catSecurity":"Security","catServices":"Services","catScheduling":"Scheduling","catPricing":"Pricing","catFollowup":"Follow-up","q1":"How do I choose the most suitable therapist for my condition?","a1":"You can use the therapists page and filter results based on exact specialty (such as anxiety, depression, or relationships), years of experience, and cost. We advise you to read the bio of each therapist and check previous customer reviews to make a decision that makes you feel comfortable and confident.","q2":"Are my sessions protected and completely confidential?","a2":"Absolutely. Confidentiality is the core of our work. All sessions take place within our encrypted environment (military-grade encryption) and we do not share any details with any third party. You can also choose text or audio sessions if you prefer not to reveal your visual identity.","q3":"What communication methods are available during sessions?","a3":"We offer three methods to suit your absolute comfort: video sessions (for direct human contact), audio sessions (for higher flexibility and privacy), and text chat sessions (to document your thoughts clearly at any time).","q4":"Can I reschedule or cancel my session?","a4":"We understand that circumstances change. You can reschedule or cancel your appointment through your dashboard or by communicating directly with the therapist, without any additional fees provided you notify them well in advance (according to the therapist's policy stated in their account).","q5":"How are session prices determined and are there any hidden costs?","a5":"Transparency is a core principle for us. The cost varies from one therapist to another based on their experience and specialty, and sessions start from 50 EGP. The price you see before booking is the final price, and there are no subscription fees or hidden costs.","q6":"Is it better to continue with the same therapist?","a6":"Yes, it is always recommended to continue with the same therapist to build a therapeutic relationship based on trust and a deep understanding of your condition. You can easily schedule regular follow-up sessions through your profile to ensure continuous progress and recovery.","allBtn":"All","noQuestions":"No questions currently available in this category.","notAnsweredTitle":"Didn't find an answer to your question?","notAnsweredDesc":"Our care and support team is always available to listen to you and respond to any inquiries you may have with complete confidentiality and respect.","contactSupportBtn":"Contact Support","nextStepsTag":"Next Steps","nextStepsTitle":"Are you ready to start?","step1Title":"Choose your therapist","step1Desc":"Browse the list of certified therapists and read reviews","step2Title":"Book your session","step2Desc":"Select your appointment and preferred communication method","step3Title":"Start Recovery","step3Desc":"Log in and start your session safely and privately"},"Therapists":{"heroBadge":"Elite Therapists","heroTitle1":"Talk to","heroTitle2":"Certified Experts","heroSubtitle":"An elite group of highly qualified psychologists, ready to help you overcome challenges and move forward in your life.","filterTitle":"Filter by Specialty","allSpecialties":"All Specialties","noTherapists":"No therapists available","noTherapistsDesc":"We couldn't find any therapists in this specialty right now. Please try another specialty.","viewAll":"View all therapists"},"Contact":{"heroBadge":"Contact Us","heroTitle1":"We are here","heroTitle2":"for you","heroSubtitle":"We are happy to listen to you. Whether you have an inquiry, a comment, or need help, our team is ready to respond to you as soon as possible.","infoTitle":"Contact Information","infoDesc":"You can contact us through any of the following channels, and we will make sure to reply within less than 24 hours.","emailTitle":"Email","emailDesc":"For general inquiries and technical support","phoneTitle":"Phone Number","phoneDesc":"Available from 9 AM to 9 PM Mecca time","addressTitle":"Headquarters","addressDesc":"Serving all parts of the Arab world digitally","responseTimeTitle":"Average Response Time","responseTimeDesc":"We understand the importance of your time, so we commit to responding to all your messages within a maximum of one hour during official working hours.","formTitle":"Send us a message","formDesc":"Please fill out the form and we will contact you shortly.","nameLabel":"Your Name","namePlaceholder":"Enter your name","emailLabel":"Email Address","emailPlaceholder":"example@domain.com","subjectLabel":"Subject","subjectOpt1":"General Inquiry","subjectOpt2":"Booking or Payment Issue","subjectOpt3":"Improvement Suggestion","subjectOpt4":"Join as a Therapist Request","subjectOpt5":"Other","messageLabel":"Message","messagePlaceholder":"How can we help you?","sendBtn":"Send Message","sending":"Sending...","successMsg":"Thank you! Your message has been successfully received. We will get back to you as soon as possible.","faqSectionTitle":"Looking for a quick answer?","faqSectionDesc":"We have compiled comprehensive answers to the most common questions. Please visit the Frequently Asked Questions page, as you might find what you are looking for right away.","faqLink":"Browse Frequently Asked Questions"},"Blog":{"post1Title":"How to choose the right therapist?","post1Desc":"A comprehensive practical guide to help you choose the therapist that fits your problem, therapeutic personality, and preferred style.","post1Cat":"Practical Tips","post1Time":"5 minutes","post2Title":"Benefits of online psychological support sessions","post2Desc":"Discover why online psychological clinics have become the first choice for many and how they achieve similar or better results.","post2Cat":"Health Info","post2Time":"7 minutes","post3Title":"Preparing for the first session with a therapist","post3Desc":"How to prepare yourself and your environment for a smoother and more effective therapeutic experience from the first session to get the most benefit.","post3Cat":"Beginner's Guide","post3Time":"6 minutes","tip1Title":"Understand your symptoms","tip1Desc":"Knowing the signs and symptoms and distinguishing between them","tip2Title":"Choosing a therapist","tip2Desc":"Clear criteria for choosing who suits you","tip3Title":"Improving the experience","tip3Desc":"Tips to get the most out of sessions","tip4Title":"Self-care","tip4Desc":"Techniques to care for yourself between sessions","heroBadge":"Reliable psychological content","heroTitle1":"Articles on","heroTitle2":"Mental Health","heroDesc":"Practical tips and health information from trusted professionals to help you understand your mental health more deeply.","catPractical":"Practical Tips","catHealth":"Health Info","catBeginner":"Beginner's Guide","latestArticles":"Latest Articles","chooseArticle":"Choose an article of interest","addRegularly":"We add new articles regularly to help you on your psychological journey.","readNow":"Read Now","whatYouFind":"What you will find in our articles","contentStrategy":"Our Content Strategy","contentStrategyDesc":"We focus on providing reliable and practical psychological content that helps you understand yourself more deeply.","newContent":"New content awaits you","newContentDesc":"We add new articles regularly. Stay in touch with us to get the latest articles and psychological tips!","contactBtn":"Contact Us","faqLink":"Or browse frequently asked questions ←"},"Privacy":{"title":"Privacy Policy","subtitle":"At Doctor Nafsy Online, we are committed to protecting your data and fully respecting your privacy. Your privacy is our responsibility.","lastUpdated":"June 2026","lastUpdatedPrefix":"Last Updated:","promise1":"We don't sell your data","promise2":"End-to-end encryption","promise3":"No sharing without permission","promise4":"Right to deletion guaranteed","ctaTitle":"Do you have a question about your data?","ctaDesc":"The support team is ready to answer any questions about your privacy and data.","contactUs":"Contact Us","sec1Title":"Data we collect","sec1Body":"We collect basic registration data such as name, email, and phone number, in addition to information related to booking and sessions to improve your experience.","sec2Title":"Use of data","sec2Body":"We use your data to provide services, communicate with you, and send updates and offers related to our services. We will not share your data with third parties without your clear permission.","sec3Title":"Security and Protection","sec3Body":"We rely on technical and organizational security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or loss, including encryption, firewalls, and HTTPS protocols.","sec4Title":"Cookies","sec4Body":"We may use cookies to improve your experience within the platform and analyze site performance. You can modify your browser preferences to control these cookies.","sec5Title":"Information sharing","sec5Body":"We only share data with necessary service providers to operate the site or upon legal request. We do not sell your data to any party under any circumstances.","sec6Title":"Your rights","sec6Body":"You can request to view, modify, or delete your data. We work to respect your requests within the applicable legal frameworks, and we will respond within 30 days.","sec7Title":"Policy updates","sec7Body":"We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes via the site or email before they are implemented.","sec8Title":"How to contact us","sec8Body":"For any questions about the privacy policy, please contact us at support@doctornafsyonline.com or phone 01010423661. Our team is ready to answer."},"Terms":{"title":"Terms and Conditions","subtitle":"By using Doctor Nafsy Online, you agree to the following terms which ensure a safe and reliable experience for all users.","lastUpdated":"June 2026","lastUpdatedPrefix":"Last Updated:","promise1":"Guaranteed Privacy","promise2":"Responsible Use","promise3":"Secure Payment","promise4":"All Rights Reserved","ctaTitle":"Do you have any questions about the terms?","ctaDesc":"We are here to clarify any unclear points to ensure your smooth use of the platform.","contactUs":"Contact Us","sec1Title":"Acceptance and Registration","sec1Body":"By registering on the platform, you acknowledge that you use correct and real data, and you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login data.","sec2Title":"Platform Rights","sec2Body":"Doctor Nafsy Online platform owns all rights to the content and services provided. It is not permissible to copy or republish any content without prior written permission.","sec3Title":"Use of Service","sec3Body":"It is forbidden to use the platform for illegal or annoying purposes. Professional conduct policy must be respected when communicating with therapists.","sec4Title":"Payment and Refund","sec4Body":"Payments are made through authorized payment channels within the platform. Refunds cannot be claimed after the start of the session except in accordance with the platform's refund policy.","sec5Title":"User Responsibility","sec5Body":"You are responsible for the information you provide during registration or during sessions. Beware of sharing any sensitive data outside the platform.","sec6Title":"Data and Content","sec6Body":"Medical and psychological content provided on the platform is general information and does not substitute personal medical or psychological diagnosis.","sec7Title":"Amendments and Notifications","sec7Body":"We reserve the right to amend these terms at any time. Amendments will be announced via the site or email.","sec8Title":"Applicable Law","sec8Body":"These terms are subject to the laws in force in the Arab Republic of Egypt, and any dispute will be resolved befor