ighly experienced therapists in treating anxiety, depression, relationships, and personal growth.","reasonTitle3":"Instant & Easy Booking","reasonDesc3":"Choose your therapist and set the appointment easily, and start your recovery journey within minutes.","featTitle1":"Fully Integrated Platform","featDesc1":"Video, audio, and chat in one secure, closed place","featTitle2":"Elite Therapists","featDesc2":"Carefully selected team to ensure the highest quality in therapy","featTitle3":"Fair Prices for All","featDesc3":"Transparent and fair pricing that matches the value provided","featTitle4":"Continuous Follow-up & Evaluation","featDesc4":"Non-stop support after the session and supportive feedback","heroTag":"Our Services","heroTitle1":"Multiple","heroTitle2":"Ways","heroTitle3":"for your mental recovery","heroDesc":"Choose the method that suits you to communicate with your certified therapist, as we provide all types of sessions in a safe and supportive environment.","servicesTag":"Therapy Packages","servicesTitle1":"Choose the method that","servicesTitle2":"suits you","servicesDesc":"We have designed three different communication methods to suit your comfort, privacy, and personal preferences.","bookBtn":"Book Your Session Now","uniquenessTag":"Uniqueness","uniquenessTitle":"What makes our platform unique?","uniquenessDesc":"We focus on the most important details of your journey: therapist quality, session security, and ease of experience.","addedValueTag":"Added Value","addedValueTitle":"Everything you need to recover","pricingTitle":"Transparent pricing reflecting true value","pricingDesc":"Prices vary depending on the therapist's specialty and experience. No subscription fees or surprises at checkout; you only pay for the session you book.","pricingCta":"View Pricing","sessionsStart":"Sessions start from","currency":"EGP","hiddenFees":"Hidden fees","zero":"Zero","paymentTransparency":"Payment Transparency"},"DashboardLayout":{"searchPlaceholder":"Search in this p